It may have been her hubby Eddie Cibrian's 40th birthday she was celebrating, but all eyes were on country crooner LeAnn Rimes (r.) as she hit the beach parading her fit form in a bright and cheery orange two-piece at a resort near Los Angeles on June 18, 2013. But she's not the only one to make a splash in a swimsuit. Not one to be outshined by Rimes, Cibrian's super sexy ex Brandi Glanville (l.) put on a show all her own while in Malibu where she was spotted strutting her stuff in a skimpy string bikini that only just managed to contain her curves.
